  - If `RCLike.im (g x) < 0`: `C - D = 0 - (-RCLike.im (g x)) = RCLike.im (g x)`

Therefore, `RHS = (A - B) + I*(C - D) = RCLike.re (g x) + I*(RCLike.im (g x)) = g x`

